 As one soldier turned to see her and Kalasin approching, he dropped his sword and ran back towards where they came in. Solari looked at Kalasin and smiled wickedly.<br>
 &quot;Would you like the honours?&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=battlingangel>Battling Angel</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://m1.cool.ne.jp/915/k_piyo00.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#993300>(3/15/03 12:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=103>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.pureshakira.com/images/gallery/shakira/aep.sized.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A debt is settled to fallen friends</span><hr size=1> Kalasin grinned. This was where she belonged, this was what she should be doing. It was a defining moment when she nodded to Solari.<br>
&quot;Of course my Queen&quot;<br>
Everything in the former Roman's mind seemed to go in slow motion as she lifted her sword above her head and threw it mercilessly at the escaping Roman soldier. The sword buried itself hilt deep in them man's back, and he fell to the ground. Together, Solari and Kalasin made their way over to the man, who was still alive. Kalasin yanked the sword out of him and turned him over so that she could see his face.<br>
Without any hint of mercy, she slashed her weapon across the mans throat, ending his life immediately.<br>
With that done, she turned back around, looking to see if there were any more men. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.camilla-nimue.com/dollz/blinkies/adopted/cookies.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=odessaofpaphos>Odessa of Paphos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 191<br> <font color=#993300>(3/15/03 10:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=104>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/xvmegvxwpt/images/amarice_11.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A debt is settled to fallen friends</span><hr size=1> Odessa caught the vile, and nodded to Aly. She turned to Solari, opening the vile, she followed Kalasin and Solari.<br>
